OL,3,CWho is Lindsay Whittle? Caerphilly's
OL,4,Cnew MS who's fought 18 elections
OL,6,FHe's definitely caused a stir in
OL,7,FCaerphilly.
OL,9,FBut his victory has been on the back
OL,10,Fburner for more than four decades.
OL,12,FLindsay Whittle is Plaid Cymru's
OL,13,Fnewest member of the Senedd. He won
OL,14,Fwith 15,961 votes ` a majority of
OL,15,F3,848, more than 47% of the total
OL,16,Fvote, which is up almost 19% from the
OL,17,F2021 result in the constituency.
