OL,3,CWho is Lindsay Whittle? Caerphilly's
OL,4,Cnew MS who's fought 18 elections
OL,6,FThe next year the miner's strikes
OL,7,Fwould begin, where Whittle says he
OL,8,Fhelped collect food for families
OL,9,Faffected by the action.
OL,11,FThe veteran politician had already
OL,12,Fbeen in politics for a number of years
OL,13,Fby then. He's served the Penyrheol
OL,14,Farea as a councillor from 1976.
OL,16,FHe was the Leader of Caerphilly
OL,17,FCouncil from 1999-2004, and again from
OL,18,F2008-2011.
