OL,3,CWho is Lindsay Whittle? Caerphilly's
OL,4,Cnew MS who's fought 18 elections
OL,6,FWhen this term ended, he got his first
OL,7,Ftaste of the Senedd, being elected as
OL,8,Fthe representative for South Wales
OL,9,FEast, serving from 2011- 2016.
OL,11,FLike his predecessor Hefin David, he
OL,12,Fis a local lad - born in Caerphilly in
OL,13,F1953.
OL,15,FOn stage at the count, he paid tribute
OL,16,Fto him, saying: "He will be a hard act
OL,17,Fto follow.
