OL,3,CWho is Lindsay Whittle? Caerphilly's
OL,4,Cnew MS who's fought 18 elections
OL,6,F"I will never fill the shoes but I
OL,7,Fpromise you I will walk the same path
OL,8,Fthat he did. I could pay no finer
OL,9,Ftribute to an excellent man."
OL,11,FBy his election to his hometown seat
OL,12,Fhe said he was "genuinely humbled."
OL,14,F"I'm a council house boy and I'm proud
OL,15,Fto call this home.
OL,17,F"The world is watching Wales, watching
OL,18,Fan emerging nation, start to control
OL,19,Four lives again."
